Looking for a golfers paradise? Our new construction homes in Bluffton put you near 40 golf courses on Hilton Head Island and in the Bluffton area. Explore Old Town Bluffton, where youll find plenty of restaurants and boutiques.

Customized New Construction Designs by Major Home Builders

When you visit new home models, you may fall in love with all the available options. From modern floor plans to the latest in hardwood floors and granite countertops, it is easy to see why people gravitate to new construction. At Pulte Homes, we believe your new home should have More Life Built In. That is why our customized homes provide you with functional home design, smart options and personalized spaces.

Our floor plans start with layouts designed to meet todays diverse desires. For example, we offer different kitchen configurations for all your needs. Whether you are looking for a kitchen filled with natural light, need a large island to house your party spread, or need ample storage for all your kitchen gadgetry youre sure to find a plan that will delight. Need a space that will change with you? Many plans feature flexible rooms that can easily become an office, playroom, or guest space depending on your needs. And all our homes come with the ability to personalize your space with our curated design selections.

Our homes also feature built-in smart home technology that helps prepare your home for todays technology needs. Our wiring helps to ensure a strong WiFi signal throughout your home, meaning you can stream your favorite shows, music, and games today and have a system that is ready for tomorrow.

Regardless of your preferred layout or style, our expert home builders are here to help bring your new dream home to life.

We Make Buying a New Home Easy

During the new construction home buying process you get to be involved in every step, from picking your finishes to watching the home being built. This is both exciting and sometimes overwhelming. Pultes team of trained associates are here to help make the process as seamless as possible.

As you evaluate home values in Bluffton and begin exploring communities online, visit our website to see our new homes for sale in the area and find a neighborhood that is perfect for you. When you are ready to learn more, our online sales specialists can help answer your questions. And, when you want to view one of our quality new construction homes, they can set a private appointment with our on-site sales consultants.

During your build, enjoy seeing the process up close with your field manager, who will be with you every step of the way. Trust your manager to let you know the progress of your home and to ensure it is built exactly to your specifications.

Need to learn more about home financing options? We can help. Check out our online Mortgage Learning Center for financial articles to help answer your simple mortgage questions. And, if you want a lender with expertise in new construction, take a look at our affiliate Pulte Mortgage. Since 1972, they have been providing quality loans to buyers looking at new construction homes.

At Pulte Homes, we make home buying easier, so you spend more time enjoying Bluffton, one of the best cities in South Carolina.

New Construction Homes Near Top Employers & Activities in Bluffton

Goal of Being Better for All

PulteGroup strives to provide a positive customer experience to all our customers through accessibility and inclusion.
Read More
New homes in Bluffton are special because they provide residents opportunities to enjoy the beautiful coastal weather. For outdoorsy people activities in Bluffton abound. Golfers will appreciate the over 40 courses scattered throughout the area; while hikers might enjoy exploring the coastal flora at the nearby Pinckney Island National Wildlife Refuge. When it is time to shop or grab a bite to eat, Old Town Bluffton offers quaint and artsy boutiques and dining opportunities that are sure to provide a lively evening.

And, when it is time to head to work in the morning, employers in Bluffton, like Gulfstream, Marriott Vacation Club International and Hilton Head Regional Medical Center offer opportunities whether your background is in aerospace, hospitality or medicine.

If Bluffton sounds like a fit for you, Pulte Homes is here to help you find the perfect new home construction community.

        Your Privacy

        When you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly identify you, but it can give you a more personalized web experience. Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer.
        California Consumer Privacy ActPrivacy Policy

        Strictly Necessary Cookies

        Always Active

        These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

        Non-Necessary Cookies

        California, Colorado, Connecticut, and Virginia residents have certain rights with respect to their data. California Residents. California residents have the right to tell us not to disclose or transfer your Personal Information to a third party in exchange for something of value. This is referred to as the opt out or do not sell or share my info right. Colorado, Connecticut, and Virginia Residents. Colorado, Connecticut, or Virginia resident, you have the right to opt out of the processing of Personal Data for the purposes of targeted advertising. How to Opt-out. As detailed in our California Privacy Policy [insert link] and our Privacy Policy [insert link], we use certain third party tracking and analytic cookies that may be considered sales and sharing of personal information. You may exercise your right to opt out of targeted advertising as well as the sale of your personal information by using the toggle switches below to disable tracking and/or analytic cookies. If you opt out we will not be able to offer you personalised ads and will not hand over your personal information to any third parties.

        • Targeting Cookies
          label

          These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.

        • Performance Cookies
          label

          These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.

        • Functional Cookies
          label

          These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.
